description:
This switch was specifically designed to provide increased overtravel, greatly improved reliability and operation. Titanium provides virtual immunity to seawater corrosion, thereby significantly increasing service life and reducing subsea maintenance and downtime costs. Titanium is used in subsea systems for its corrosion resistance, maintenance reduction, and its mechanical property advantages. With titanium reliably is improved.

Options:
1) Custom configurations are available.
3) Can be supplied with a molded underwater cable and connector or PBOF (pressure balanced oil filled) adapter, straight or right angle.
4) Can be made in stainless steel for cost savings.
